> **Note:** If you configured an external source folder (e.g., `D:\OneDrive\Photos`) in Step 2, your photos are already there - no copying needed.
>
> Folder structure becomes gallery structure on the website. The `01` prefix controls the navigation order.
>
> **Categories:** Top-level folders like `01 Galleries` become navigation categories. Subfolders become galleries within that category.

